    </div>

    <p>
      Our two robots, 4744A and 4744B, achieved strong results at the VEX regional competition in Tokyo, Japan. 
	  Robot 4744B won the tournament and performed successfully in the skills challenge, and robot 4744A received the Design Award. 
	  These results qualified our team for the VEX World Championship in California, USA, later that year. 
    </p>

